title: Paris Hilton Heiress Women Eau De Parfum Spray, 1 Ounce
description: Paris Hilton Heiress By Paris Hilton Eau De Parfum Spray 1 Oz For Women : It has top notes of passion fruit, orange, peach granita, and champagne mimosa. With middle notes consisting of star jasmine, tiare flower, ylang-ylang, honeysuckle, dewberry blossom, and grenadine. Then base notes of violet leaf, vetiver, tonka, and blonde woods.

title: Lucky 6 By Liz Claiborne For Women. Eau De Parfum Spray 3.4 Oz.
description: Launched by the design house of Lucky Brand.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied
